{
  "page": "Unicorn",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:252px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Unicorn_by_Kevin_Catalan.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/2/2e/Unicorn_by_Kevin_Catalan.jpg/250px-Unicorn_by_Kevin_Catalan.jpg\" width=\"250\" height=\"350\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/2/2e/Unicorn_by_Kevin_Catalan.jpg/375px-Unicorn_by_Kevin_Catalan.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/2/2e/Unicorn_by_Kevin_Catalan.jpg/500px-Unicorn_by_Kevin_Catalan.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Unicorn_by_Kevin_Catalan.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>A unicorn, by Kevin Catalan ©</div></div></div>\n<p>A <b>unicorn</b> is a large goat-like <a href=\"/index.php/Animal\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Animal\">animal</a>, with a long single horn on its head. Unicorns are believed to live on <a href=\"/index.php/Skagos\" title=\"Skagos\">Skagos</a>,<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc15.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc15.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd9.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd9.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> and some claim unicorns can be found in the higher mountains of <a href=\"/index.php/Ib\" title=\"Ib\">Ib</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf837_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf837-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> Sure-footed unicorns can climb steep mountains.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf713_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf713-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Culture\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Culture</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#A_Feast_for_Crows\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Feast for Crows</i></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Quotes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#External_links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External links</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Culture\">Culture</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Unicorn&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Culture\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:202px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Brax.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/5/54/House_Brax.svg/200px-House_Brax.svg.png\" width=\"200\" height=\"220\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/5/54/House_Brax.svg/300px-House_Brax.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/5/54/House_Brax.svg/400px-House_Brax.svg.png 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Brax.svg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>The <a href=\"/index.php/House_Brax\" title=\"House Brax\">House Brax</a> coat of arms features a unicorn.</div></div></div>\n<p>There are ancient tales of <a href=\"/index.php/Hairy_Men\" title=\"Hairy Men\">Hairy Men</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/Essos\" title=\"Essos\">Essos</a> riding unicorns to battle,<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf835_5-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf835-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup> and <a href=\"/index.php/Skagosi\" title=\"Skagosi\">Skagosi</a> lords are also said to ride unicorns.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf713_4-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf713-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Stone sentries outside of the shop of <a href=\"/index.php/Tobho_Mott\" title=\"Tobho Mott\">Tobho Mott</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a> are decorated as <a href=\"/index.php/Griffin\" title=\"Griffin\">griffin</a> and unicorn knights.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot27.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot27.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Several <a href=\"/index.php/Westerosi\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Westerosi\">Westerosi</a> houses feature <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Unicorn#Heraldry\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Unicorn\">heraldic unicorns</a> in their sigils, including Houses <a href=\"/index.php/House_Brax\" title=\"House Brax\">Brax</a>,<sup id=\"cite_ref-west_7-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-west-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup> <a href=\"/index.php/House_Doggett\" title=\"House Doggett\">Doggett</a>,<sup id=\"cite_ref-west_7-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-west-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup> <a href=\"/index.php/House_Rogers\" title=\"House Rogers\">Rogers</a>,<sup id=\"cite_ref-8\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-8\">&#91;8&#93;</a></sup> and <a href=\"/index.php/House_Wydman\" title=\"House Wydman\">Wydman</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-9\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-9\">&#91;9&#93;</a></sup> Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Flement_Brax\" title=\"Flement Brax\">Flement Brax</a> decorates his horsehead helm with a long spiral horn.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot56.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_10-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot56.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-10\">&#91;10&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Dishonest traders sometimes sell \"unicorn horns\" which are actually the tusks of narwhals hunted by the <a href=\"/index.php/Ibbenese\" title=\"Ibbenese\">Ibbenese</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf713_4-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf713-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Unicorn&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Feast_for_Crows\"><i>A Feast for Crows</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Unicorn&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Feast for Crows\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Samwell_Tarly\" title=\"Samwell Tarly\">Samwell Tarly</a> recalls having read that the Skagosi ride great shaggy unicorns to war.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc15.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc15.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Unicorn horns are amongst plunder brought from distant lands by <a href=\"/index.php/Euron_Greyjoy\" title=\"Euron Greyjoy\">Euron Greyjoy</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc29.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_11-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc29.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-11\">&#91;11&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Unicorn&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Dance with Dragons\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Snow\" title=\"Jon Snow\">Jon Snow</a>, in a dream as his <a href=\"/index.php/Direwolf\" title=\"Direwolf\">direwolf</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Ghost\" title=\"Ghost\">Ghost</a>, sees that <a href=\"/index.php/Shaggydog\" title=\"Shaggydog\">Shaggydog</a> has fought and killed what may be a unicorn.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd3.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_12-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd3.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-12\">&#91;12&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>In the <a href=\"/index.php/Cave_of_the_three-eyed_crow\" title=\"Cave of the three-eyed crow\">cave of the three-eyed crow</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Leaf\" title=\"Leaf\">Leaf</a> tells <a href=\"/index.php/Bran_Stark\" title=\"Bran Stark\">Bran Stark</a> that the unicorns are all but gone.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_13-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-13\">&#91;13&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Among some of the tribute collected from the <a href=\"/index.php/Free_folk\" title=\"Free folk\">free folk</a> passing through the <a href=\"/index.php/Wall\" title=\"Wall\">Wall</a> is a helm made with a unicorn’s head.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd58.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_14-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd58.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-14\">&#91;14&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:252px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Unicornis.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/b/b0/Unicornis.jpg/250px-Unicornis.jpg\" width=\"250\" height=\"177\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/b/b0/Unicornis.jpg/375px-Unicornis.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/b/b0/Unicornis.jpg/500px-Unicornis.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Unicornis.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Real-world woodcut depicting a unicorn, circa 13th century</div></div></div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes\">Quotes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Unicorn&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>A wild rain lashed down upon <a href=\"/index.php/Shaggydog\" title=\"Shaggydog\">his black brother</a> as he tore at the flesh of an enormous goat, washing the blood from his side where the goat's long horn had raked him.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd3.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_12-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd3.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-12\">&#91;12&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;dreams of <a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Snow\" title=\"Jon Snow\">Jon Snow</a> as <a href=\"/index.php/Ghost\" title=\"Ghost\">Ghost</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Unicorn&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap mw-references-columns\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Raffc15.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc15.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc15.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows-Chapter_15\" title=\"A Feast for Crows-Chapter 15\">Chapter 15</a>, Samwell II.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd9.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd9.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_9\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 9\">Chapter 9</a>, Davos I.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiaf837-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiaf837_3-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, Beyond the Sunset Kingdom&#58; Beyond the Free Cities&#32;(Ib).</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiaf713-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiaf713_4-0\">4.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiaf713_4-1\">4.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiaf713_4-2\">4.2</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, The Seven Kingdoms&#5